# Runtime data — rebuild with `npm run db:init && npm run db:seed-chart && python3 scripts/enrich.py`
# The SQLite DB holds Musixmatch-licensed lyrics, so it stays out of git.
data/
# ...except the hand-curated chart seed (source code, no licensing issue)
!data/chart-seed.ts
# ...the offline snapshots (lyrics + signals + graph) so the project can
# run after the Musixmatch / Genius / Wikidata APIs become unavailable
!data/snapshots/
# ...and the runtime logs (gitignored, but kept locally for debug)
!data/logs/
data/logs/

